{"type":"answer","id":102586,"parentType":"question","parentId":13104,"uid":23499,"contents":"喜欢<br>\n<br>\n有秘密后院的粉丝吗？我喜欢他们的《春去秋来》《梦生》《梦》，每次听心里都很平静。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://www.zhengjian.org/node/102640\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《大唐的记忆》</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.zhengjian.org/node/102421\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">《风动铃动心不动》</a>，这两首是我的单曲循环。<br>\n<br>\n但是不知道算不算轻音乐。<br>\n<br>\n还有《拥舞在天际》、班得瑞《早晨的空气》、邵容《<i>Bamboo Dance</i>》……<br>\n<br>\n我还尤其喜欢 水晶琴 演奏的轻（纯）音乐，我的上网背景音乐。","date":"2019-12-12","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}